{"tid":2225350,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla減價｜中國Model 3減8% 起跳價24.99萬人幣 用寧德時代電池慳成本","createTime":"2020-10-01T08:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:21:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":36,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"bfefa67fac7838baa261a846949edb2f24c0c8b0","tid":2225350,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"綜合外電指出，Tesla中國產的Model 3電動車預計使用寧德時代生產的無鈷磷酸鐵鋰（LFP）電池。這種電池的原物料價格更低，因此容許中國版Model 3的起跳價降低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201001/ZX4ZWMA2XJBLBB23ZEB2GOGGIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201001%2FZX4ZWMA2XJBLBB23ZEB2GOGGIE%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w11znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=ad2886f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201001%2FZX4ZWMA2XJBLBB23ZEB2GOGGIE%2F&h=09bd530f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201001/ZX4ZWMA2XJBLBB23ZEB2GOGGIE/</a>"},{"pid":"7aa3b2ad13ec9aec76e6091141129f20d9a3ffdf","tid":2225350,"uid":260371,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"等睇中國特供版特斯拉爆炸"},{"pid":"dda7a0d47d2b64cd1d0ca46af73acfa19a23c030","tid":2225350,"uid":25900,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"香港買既話都係支版？"},{"pid":"2f5f531df666e132c0a4c3a72c139f33be39ea55","tid":2225350,"uid":19725,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"如果港版扣稅後24 萬又抵玩"},{"pid":"11a035c50787d44c6785c03dd448f0ad1d47f442","tid":2225350,"uid":49853,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"dda7a0d47d2b64cd1d0ca46af73acfa19a23c030","tid":2225350,"uid":25900,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"香港買既話都係支版？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"據 Reuters 報導指，位於上海的 Tesla 中國廠房雖然現在只生產用於在中國銷售的電動車，但 Tesla 計劃在明年開始向日本和香港等地提供中國製 Model 3，而除了日本和香港之外，上海廠房製造的 Tesla 電動車未來也會向其他的歐洲和亞洲地區提供。"},{"pid":"c235c14939c5fd17666b8c1ca54c2ccce81bfa5a","tid":2225350,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"我們在美國的父，願人都尊你的名為ironmam，願你的space X降臨，願你的model X，行在地上，如同starlink行在天上。我們晚晚炒的tsla，今日分拆給我們；接上我們的大腦，如同我們接上電腦的接口。不要叫我們遇見熊市，救我們脫離貧窮；因為火星，地球，月球，全是你的，直到永遠。阿門。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntsla禱告區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2187782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2187782</a>"},{"pid":"bf1d3f0059d93785a1a19d6d11cdc1509e636b00","tid":2225350,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"粒電唔得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eb0d943e9a43846520be427fe2d6e7a25b7b99","tid":2225350,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf1d3f0059d93785a1a19d6d11cdc1509e636b00","tid":2225350,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"粒電唔得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"支版足矣"},{"pid":"63fcb41a8b150378e93b43af69d8975e55115e2a","tid":2225350,"uid":257041,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf1d3f0059d93785a1a19d6d11cdc1509e636b00","tid":2225350,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"粒電唔得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"得嘅就唔駛減價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f86d09a7338ef5d6cf75b199daf9b23bd